{"tid":2017850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄違反毛主席教誨，嚴重損害我國同胞感情","createTime":"2020-05-15T09:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T10:14:27.000Z","uid":46904,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d6836e3842207aa635baf778cf981cd2be520dad","tid":2017850,"uid":46904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pVOuF3r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpVOuF3r.jpg&h=b151241c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想轉載楊Sir言論去百度比同胞們討論一下<br />\n楊潤雄同志貴為教育局局長<br />\n竟然公開指出日本侵華對中國發展只有害無利<br />\n實在有違先師毛主席的教誨<br />\n嚴重損害我國同胞感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n翻查楊Sir背景，原來其子女留學澳洲<br />\n及其對中共歷史之淺薄認識<br />\n實在令人懷疑楊Sir是叛國者之嫌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我認為有必要把楊Sir言論轉載到微博及百度<br />\n讓內地愛國愛黨同胞提防此人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/okoa9ZJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fokoa9ZJ.png&h=1b0be45a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jzvpu0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJzvpu0b.jpg&h=df51dc3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：我愛中國，對楊Sir言論真係好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36bf9fa7feaf77d20d77e456f6fa958560b1819","tid":2017850,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T10:07:09.000Z","msg":"日本侵華係對中華人民共和國利大於弊,但對中華民國弊大於利,可能佢地一中定義係一個中國,中華民國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b99c7e30bfcd5f6ab6c3fde5cba2a61941cfd21","tid":2017850,"uid":46904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a36bf9fa7feaf77d20d77e456f6fa958560b1819","tid":2017850,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T10:07:09.000Z","msg":"日本侵華係對中華人民共和國利大於弊,但對中華民國弊大於利,可能佢地一中定義係一個中國,中華民國<img src=\"/ass